# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

---------------------------------

## 2017-09-05
Born of the project

---------------------------------

## 2017-09-08
Main release with the principal functions implemented

---------------------------------

## 2017-09-11

### Added

- Use of the same configuration JSON for many hostnames and users using the '*'
  marker

---------------------------------

## 2017-09-21

### Added

- Project totally redesigned using objects
- Info box with auto-split text and multi text

### Removed

- Customizable text for interface (english is enought)

---------------------------------

## 2017-09-22

### Added

- Interactive installer with Python interpreter recognition

---------------------------------

## 2017-09-27

### Added

- Use of environment variables into commands path of the user configuration
  JSON, indicated as usual with a "$" followed by the variable name
